00:47:59.166 --> 00:48:02.028
or "vessel"
also means "thing,"

00:48:02.028 --> 00:48:04.757
skuos,
that's what Paul uses there,

00:48:04.757 --> 00:48:05.969
control your thing.
 

00:48:05.969 --> 00:48:09.226
Now does "thing"
refer to his body,

00:48:09.226 --> 00:48:11.889
his wife's body,
or his genitalia?

00:48:11.889 --> 00:48:14.737
It's anybody's guess,
and different interpreters

00:48:14.737 --> 00:48:17.949
disagree about how they would
want to translate it.

00:48:17.949 --> 00:48:21.793
What it certainly shows is that
Paul's addressing a group of

00:48:21.793 --> 00:48:24.327
men,
and one scholar from Copenhagen

00:48:24.327 --> 00:48:27.010
has written an article where she
says,

00:48:27.010 --> 00:48:28.460
we ought to take this seriously.
 

00:48:28.460 --> 00:48:30.976
At least at this stage in
Paul's career,

00:48:30.976 --> 00:48:34.784
maybe he really did see these
groups as being primarily male

00:48:34.784 --> 00:48:35.429
clubs.
 

00:48:35.429 --> 00:48:39.224
Sure, they may have had women
and daughters and wives as part

00:48:39.224 --> 00:48:42.326
of them in a way,
but maybe in Paul's conception

00:48:42.326 --> 00:48:45.079
these things were sort of like
fraternities.

00:48:45.079 --> 00:48:49.121
The fraternity of Jesus,
and that's why he addresses

00:48:49.121 --> 00:48:52.530
only men and he doesn't talk
about women.

00:48:52.530 --> 00:48:55.280
And that's why when he's
talking about--

00:48:55.280 --> 00:48:59.034
and these are a fraternity that
seem not to have expected the

00:48:59.034 --> 00:49:02.099
resurrection and all this other
kind of stuff,

00:49:02.099 --> 00:49:05.739
so Paul writes 1 Thessalonians
to clue them in on it.

00:49:05.739 --> 00:49:11.351
What this would be would be a
male club of Greek speaking,

00:49:11.351 --> 00:49:14.010
Gentile, manual laborers.
 

00:49:14.010 --> 00:49:19.878
They've now been initiated into
a new group that demands

00:49:19.878 --> 00:49:26.172
adherence and loyalty to the God
of the Jews and an expected

00:49:26.172 --> 00:49:28.199
Jewish Messiah.
 

00:49:28.199 --> 00:49:34.945
In other words,
this is an apocalyptic Jewish

00:49:34.945 --> 00:49:37.860
sect of Gentiles.
 

